DealSurf,is,a,daily,deal,aggregator,service,It,offers,deals,from,hundreds,of,providers,including,LivingSocial,kgb,Deals,GroupOn,and,more,The,API,exposes,site,data,that,developers,can,integrate,into,their,own,web,sites,or,applications,Functionality,includes,returning,today,s,daily,deals,in,a,specified,city,and,returning,deals,by,ID,The,API,uses,RESTful,calls,and,responses,are,formatted,in,XML,and,JSON